DeconvoliSTa
============

DeconvoliSTa is a Snakemake-based spatial-transcriptomics deconvolution
benchmark pipeline with an interactive visualization, developed at the
Centre de Bioinformatique de Bordeaux (CBiB), University of Bordeaux, France.

Derived work
------------
DeconvoliSTa is derived from and extends the spotless-benchmark project:

    spotless-benchmark — Chananchida Sang-aram et al.
    https://github.com/csangara/spotless-benchmark

